722
00:55:27.760 --> 00:55:29.000
Huh?

723
00:55:29.080 --> 00:55:32.000
Hey, you're stirring up the water, dude.

724
00:55:32.080 --> 00:55:34.920
Yeah, try not to scare off
the fish there, buddy.

725
00:55:35.440 --> 00:55:36.880
-Uh...
-KODA: Tug.

726
00:55:36.960 --> 00:55:39.640
Hey, Koda. Come here.

727
00:55:40.240 --> 00:55:41.720
Look at you.

728
00:55:42.320 --> 00:55:46.400
-Have you seen my mom yet?
-No, as a matter of fact I haven't.

729
00:55:47.280 --> 00:55:51.000
-Me and my friend Kenai beat her.
-He's with you?

730
00:55:51.680 --> 00:55:53.600
Uh... Hi.

731
00:55:54.640 --> 00:55:58.120
Huh. I've never seen you
at the run before.

732
00:55:58.200 --> 00:56:02.000
-Where are you from?
-(STAMMERS) Well, I...

733
00:56:02.080 --> 00:56:04.960
There's the mountain,
just like I promised.

734
00:56:05.040 --> 00:56:07.120
The lights touch the top every night.

735
00:56:07.960 --> 00:56:10.920
Gonna be harder getting up there
than riding those mammoths.

736
00:56:11.000 --> 00:56:12.720
-Mammoths?
-Are you kidding?

737
