Koda. Koda. (CLEARS THROAT)

741
00:56:24.720 --> 00:56:27.720
Can I talk to you for a second?
Excuse us.

742
00:56:28.520 --> 00:56:31.360
Hmm. He's kind of jumpy, isn't he?

743
00:56:31.440 --> 00:56:33.560
Okay. Okay. (NERVOUS LAUGH)

744
00:56:33.720 --> 00:56:35.440
Koda, I, uh...

745
00:56:36.160 --> 00:56:40.160
-Uh, I got to get going.
-Well, when you come back...

746
00:56:40.240 --> 00:56:42.400
I... I won't be coming back.

747
00:56:42.480 --> 00:56:44.560
What? Why not?

748
00:56:46.040 --> 00:56:49.080
Because... Well, it's hard to...

749
00:56:49.160 --> 00:56:51.360
-You're leaving?
-(SHOUTS) No.

750
00:56:51.440 --> 00:56:53.680
(STAMMERS) Well, I mean, yes.

751
00:56:53.760 --> 00:56:56.120
Well, it's just that I...

752
00:56:56.200 --> 00:56:59.600
-I don't belong here.
-Don't belong?

753
00:56:59.680 --> 00:57:03.600
Every bear belongs here.
Come on, buddy.

754
00:57:03.680 --> 00:57:04.840
<i>Everyone's invited</i>

755
00:57:04.920 --> 00:57:06.080
Let's have some fun!

756
00:57:06.160 --> 00:57:08.360
<i>This is how we live</i>

757
00:57:10.440 --> 00:57:12.680
<i>We're all here for each other</i>

758
00:57:14.320 --> 00:57:16.360
<i>Happy to give</i>

759
00:57:18.160 --> 00:57:20.960
<i>All we have, we share</i>

760
00:57:21.800 --> 00:57:24.800
<i>And all of us, we care</i>

761
00:57:24.880 --> 00:57:26.280
<i>So come on</i>

762
